<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc839397-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s132"><num value="132">§ 132.</num><heading> Departments of Library</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Library of Congress shall be arranged in two departments, a general library and a law library.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc839398-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(R.S. § 81.)</sourceCredit>
